u Jour de la Résurrection, de vous accorder ce que vous jugerez devoir obtenir ?","en":"Or do you have oaths [binding] upon Us, extending until the Day of Resurrection, that indeed for you is whatever you judge?","words":[{"position":1,"ar":"أَمْ","fr":"Ou","en":"Or","tr":"am","isWaqf":false},{"position":2,"ar":"لَكُمْ","fr":"pour vous","en":"for you","tr":"lakum","isWaqf":false},{"position":3,"ar":"أَيْمَـٰنٌ","fr":"serments","en":"oaths","tr":"aymānun","isWaqf":false},{"position":4,"ar":"عَلَيْنَا","fr":"de nous","en":"from us","tr":"ʿalaynā","isWaqf":false},{"position":5,"ar":"بَـٰلِغَةٌ","fr":"atteignant","en":"reaching","tr":"bālighatun","isWaqf":false},{"position":6,"ar":"إِلَىٰ","fr":"à","en":"to","tr":"ilā","isWaqf":false},{"position":7,"ar":"يَوْمِ","fr":"(le) Jour","en":"(the) Day","tr":"yawmi","isWaqf":false},{"position":8,"ar":"ٱلْقِيَـٰمَةِ ۙ","fr":"(de la) Résurrection","en":"(of) the Resurrection","tr":"l-qiyāmati","isWaqf":false},{"position":9,"ar":"إِنَّ","fr":"certes","en":"indeed","tr":"inna","isWaqf":false},{"position":10,"ar":"لَكُمْ","fr":"pour vous","en":"for you","tr":"lakum","isWaqf":false},{"position":11,"ar":"لَمَا","fr":"(est) ce que","en":"(is) what","tr":"lamā","isWaqf":false},{"position":12,"ar":"تَحْكُمُونَ","fr":"vous jugez","en":"you judge","tr":"taḥkumūna","isWaqf":false}]},{"ayah":40,"verseKey":"68:40","juz":29,"arabic":"سَلْهُمْ أَيُّهُم بِذَٰلِكَ زَعِيمٌ","fr":"Demande-leur lequel d’entre eux en serait garant ?","en":"Ask them which of them, for that [claim], is responsible.","words":[{"position":1,"ar":"سَلْهُمْ","fr":"Demander eux","en":"Ask them","tr":"salhum","isWaqf":false},{"position":2,"ar":"أَيُّهُم","fr":"que d’eux","en":"which of them","tr":"ayyuhum","isWaqf":false},{"position":3,"ar":"بِذَٰلِكَ","fr":"pour que","en":"for that","tr":"bidhālika","isWaqf":false},{"position":4,"ar":"زَعِيمٌ","fr":"(est) responsable","en":"(is) responsible","tr":"zaʿīmun","isWaqf":false}]},{"ayah":41,"verseKey":"68:41","juz":29,"arabic":"أَمْ لَهُمْ شُرَكَآءُ فَلْيَأْتُوا۟ بِشُرَكَآئِهِمْ إِن كَانُوا۟ صَـٰدِقِينَ","fr":"Ou alors auraient-ils des associés ? Qu’ils les amènent donc, si ce qu’ils disent est vrai !","en":"Or do they have partners? Then let them bring their partners, if they should be truthful.","words":[{"position":1,"ar":"أَمْ","fr":"Ou","en":"Or","tr":"am","isWaqf":false},{"position":2,"ar":"لَهُمْ","fr":"(sont) pour eux","en":"(are) for them","tr":"lahum","isWaqf":false},{"position":3,"ar":"شُرَكَآءُ","fr":"associés","en":"partners","tr":"shurakāu","isWaqf":false},{"position":4,"ar":"فَلْيَأْتُوا۟","fr":"Puis laisser eux apporter","en":"Then let them bring","tr":"falyatū","isWaqf":false},{"position":5,"ar":"بِشُرَكَآئِهِمْ","fr":"leur associés","en":"their partners","tr":"bishurakāihim","isWaqf":false},{"position":6,"ar":"إِن","fr":"si","en":"if","tr":"in","isWaqf":false},{"position":7,"ar":"كَانُوا۟","fr":"ils sont","en":"they are","tr":"kānū","isWaqf":false},{"position":8,"ar":"صَـٰدِقِينَ","fr":"véridique","en":"truthful","tr":"ṣādiqīna","isWaqf":false}]},{"ayah":42,"verseKey":"68:42","juz":29,"arabic":"يَوْمَ يُكْشَفُ عَن سَاقٍ وَيُدْعَوْنَ إِلَى ٱلسُّجُودِ فَلَا يَسْتَطِيعُونَ","fr":"Le jour où ils auront à affronter la Grande Peur, ils seront appelés à se prosterner mais ils ne le pourront pas.","en":"The Day the shin will be uncovered and they are invited to prostration but they [i.e., the disbelievers] will not be able,","words":[{"position":1,"ar":"يَوْمَ","fr":"(Le) Jour","en":"(The) Day","tr":"yawma","isWaqf":false},{"position":2,"ar":"يُكْشَفُ","fr":"va être découvrit","en":"will be uncovered","tr":"yuk'shafu","isWaqf":false},{"position":3,"ar":"عَن","fr":"de","en":"from","tr":"ʿan","isWaqf":false},{"position":4,"ar":"سَاقٍۢ","fr":"le shin","en":"the shin","tr":"sāqin","isWaqf":false},{"position":5,"ar":"وَيُدْعَوْنَ","fr":"et ils va être appelé","en":"and they will be called","tr":"wayud'ʿawna","isWaqf":false},{"position":6,"ar":"إِلَى","fr":"à","en":"to","tr":"ilā","isWaqf":false},{"position":7,"ar":"ٱلسُّجُودِ","fr":"se prosterner","en":"prostrate","tr":"l-sujūdi","isWaqf":false},{"position":8,"ar":"فَلَا","fr":"mais non","en":"but not","tr":"falā","isWaqf":false},{"position":9,"ar":"يَسْتَطِيعُونَ","fr":"ils va être capable","en":"they will be able","tr":"yastaṭīʿūna","isWaqf":false}]},{"ayah":43,"verseKey":"68:43","juz":29,"arabic":"خَـٰشِعَةً أَبْصَـٰرُهُمْ تَرْهَقُهُمْ ذِلَّةٌ ۖ وَقَدْ كَانُوا۟ يُدْعَوْنَ إِلَى ٱلسُّجُودِ وَهُمْ سَـٰلِمُونَ","fr":"Baissés seront leurs regards, et ils seront couverts d’humiliation, eux qu’on invitait autrefois à se prosterner quand ils étaient sains !","en":"Their eyes humbled, humiliation will cover them. And they used to be invited to prostration while they were sound.","words":[{"position":1,"ar":"خَـٰشِعَةً","fr":"Humilié","en":"Humbled","tr":"khāshiʿatan","isWaqf":false},{"position":2,"ar":"أَبْصَـٰرُهُمْ","fr":"leurs yeux","en":"their eyes","tr":"abṣāruhum","isWaqf":false},{"position":3,"ar":"تَرْهَقُهُمْ","fr":"va couvrir eux","en":"will cover them","tr":"tarhaquhum","isWaqf":false},{"position":4,"ar":"ذِلَّةٌۭ ۖ","fr":"humiliation","en":"humiliation","tr":"dhillatun","isWaqf":false},{"position":5,"ar":"وَقَدْ","fr":"Et certes","en":"And indeed","tr":"waqad","isWaqf":false},{"position":6,"ar":"كَانُوا۟","fr":"ils étaient","en":"they were","tr":"kānū","isWaqf":false},{"position":7,"ar":"يُدْعَوْنَ","fr":"appelé","en":"called","tr":"yud'ʿawna","isWaqf":false},{"position":8,"ar":"إِلَى","fr":"à","en":"to","tr":"ilā","isWaqf":false},{"position":9,"ar":"ٱلسُّجُودِ","fr":"se prosterner","en":"prostrate","tr":"l-sujūdi","isWaqf":false},{"position":10,"ar":"وَهُمْ","fr":"tandis qu'ils","en":"while they","tr":"wahum","isWaqf":false},{"position":11,"ar":"سَـٰلِمُونَ","fr":"(étaient) son","en":"(were) sound","tr":"sālimūna","isWaqf":false}]},{"ayah":44,"verseKey":"68:44","juz":29,"arabic":"فَذَرْنِى وَمَن يُكَذِّبُ بِهَـٰذَا ٱلْحَدِيثِ ۖ سَنَسْتَدْرِجُهُم مِّنْ حَيْثُ لَا يَعْلَمُونَ","fr":"Laisse-Moi donc avec ceux qui nient cette Parole (le Coran). Nous les amènerons de proche en proche (à leur ruine), sans qu’ils ne sachent (de quelle façon).","en":"So leave Me, [O Muḥammad], with [the matter of] whoever denies this statement [i.e., the Qur’ān]. We will progressively lead them [to punishment] from where they do not know.","words":[{"position":1,"ar":"فَذَرْنِى","fr":"Donc quitter Moi","en":"So leave Me","tr":"fadharnī","isWaqf":false},{"position":2,"ar":"وَمَن","fr":"et quiconque","en":"and whoever","tr":"waman","isWaqf":false},{"position":3,"ar":"يُكَذِّبُ","fr":"nie","en":"denies","tr":"yukadhibu","isWaqf":false},{"position":4,"ar":"بِهَـٰذَا","fr":"ceci","en":"this","tr":"bihādhā","isWaqf":false},{"position":5,"ar":"ٱلْحَدِيثِ ۖ","fr":"Parole","en":"Statement","tr":"l-ḥadīthi","isWaqf":false},{"position":6,"ar":"سَنَسْتَدْرِجُهُم","fr":"Nous va progressivement mener eux","en":"We will progressively lead them","tr":"sanastadrijuhum","isWaqf":false},{"position":7,"ar":"مِّنْ","fr":"de","en":"from","tr":"min","isWaqf":false},{"position":8,"ar":"حَيْثُ","fr":"où","en":"where","tr":"ḥaythu","isWaqf":false},{"position":9,"ar":"لَا","fr":"non","en":"not","tr":"lā","isWaqf":false},{"position":10,"ar":"يَعْلَمُونَ","fr":"ils savent","en":"they know","tr":"yaʿlamūna","isWaqf":false}]},{"ayah":45,"verseKey":"68:45","juz":29,"arabic":"وَأُمْلِى لَهُمْ ۚ إِنَّ كَيْدِى مَتِينٌ","fr":"Je leur accorderai un répit, car Ma Ruse est infaillible.","en":"And I will give them time. Indeed, My plan is firm.","words":[{"position":1,"ar":"وَأُمْلِى","fr":"Et Je va donner répit","en":"And I will give respite","tr":"wa-um'lī","isWaqf":false},{"position":2,"ar":"لَهُمْ ۚ","fr":"à eux","en":"to them","tr":"lahum","isWaqf":false},{"position":3,"ar":"إِنَّ","fr":"Certes","en":"Indeed","tr":"inna","isWaqf":false},{"position":4,"ar":"كَيْدِى","fr":"Mon planifier","en":"My plan","tr":"kaydī","isWaqf":false},{"position":5,"ar":"مَتِينٌ","fr":"(est) ferme","en":"(is) firm","tr":"matīnun","isWaqf":false}]},{"ayah":46,"verseKey":"68:46","juz":29,"arabic":"أَمْ تَسْـَٔلُهُمْ أَجْرًا فَهُم مِّن مَّغْرَمٍ مُّثْقَلُونَ","fr":"Leur réclamerais-tu une récompense qui les grèverait d’une lourde dette ?","en":"Or do you ask of them a payment, so they are by debt burdened down?","words":[{"position":1,"ar":"أَمْ","fr":"Ou","en":"Or","tr":"am","isWaqf":false},{"position":2,"ar":"تَسْـَٔلُهُمْ","fr":"vous les interrogez","en":"you ask them","tr":"tasaluhum","isWaqf":false},{"position":3,"ar":"أَجْرًۭا","fr":"un paiement","en":"a payment","tr":"ajran","isWaqf":false},{"position":4,"ar":"فَهُم","fr":"donc ils","en":"so they","tr":"fahum","isWaqf":false},{"position":5,"ar":"مِّن","fr":"de","en":"from","tr":"min","isWaqf":false},{"position":6,"ar":"مَّغْرَمٍۢ","fr":"(le) dette","en":"(the) debt","tr":"maghramin","isWaqf":false},{"position":7,"ar":"مُّثْقَلُونَ","fr":"(sont) chargé","en":"(are) burdened","tr":"muth'qalūna","isWaqf":false}]},{"ayah":47,"verseKey":"68:47","juz":29,"arabic":"أَمْ عِندَهُمُ ٱلْغَيْبُ فَهُمْ يَكْتُبُونَ","fr":"Détiendraient-ils les clefs de l’Inconnaissable (ghayb) qui leur permettraient d’imposer (leurs fausses croyances) par écrit ?","en":"Or have they [knowledge of] the unseen, so they write [it] down?","words":[{"position":1,"ar":"أَمْ","fr":"Ou","en":"Or","tr":"am","isWaqf":false},{"position":2,"ar":"عِندَهُمُ","fr":"(est) avec eux","en":"(is) with them","tr":"ʿindahumu","isWaqf":false},{"position":3,"ar":"ٱلْغَيْبُ","fr":"l’invisible","en":"the unseen","tr":"l-ghaybu","isWaqf":false},{"position":4,"ar":"فَهُمْ","fr":"donc ils","en":"so they","tr":"fahum","isWaqf":false},{"position":5,"ar":"يَكْتُبُونَ","fr":"écrire cela","en":"write it","tr":"yaktubūna","isWaqf":false}]},{"ayah":48,"verseKey":"68:48","juz":29,"arabic":"فَٱصْبِرْ لِحُكْمِ رَبِّكَ وَلَا تَكُن كَصَاحِبِ ٱلْحُوتِ إِذْ نَادَىٰ وَهُوَ مَكْظُومٌ","fr":"Supporte patiemment le Verdict de ton Seigneur ! Ne sois pas comme l’Homme au Poisson quand, en pleine angoisse, il adressa sa plainte (à Allah).","en":"Then be patient for the decision of your Lord, [O Muḥammad], and be not like the companion of the fish [i.e., Jonah] when he called out while he was distressed.","words":[{"position":1,"ar":"فَٱصْبِرْ","fr":"Sois donc patient","en":"So be patient","tr":"fa-iṣ'bir","isWaqf":false},{"position":2,"ar":"لِحُكْمِ","fr":"pour (le) décision","en":"for (the) decision","tr":"liḥuk'mi","isWaqf":false},{"position":3,"ar":"رَبِّكَ","fr":"(de) votre Seigneur","en":"(of) your Lord","tr":"rabbika","isWaqf":false},{"position":4,"ar":"وَلَا","fr":"et (fais) non","en":"and (do) not","tr":"walā","isWaqf":false},{"position":5,"ar":"تَكُن","fr":"être","en":"be","tr":"takun","isWaqf":false},{"position":6,"ar":"كَصَاحِبِ","fr":"comme (le) compagnon","en":"like (the) companion","tr":"kaṣāḥibi","isWaqf":false},{"position":7,"ar":"ٱلْحُوتِ","fr":"(de) le poisson","en":"(of) the fish","tr":"l-ḥūti","isWaqf":false},{"position":8,"ar":"إِذْ","fr":"quand","en":"when","tr":"idh","isWaqf":false},{"position":9,"ar":"نَادَىٰ","fr":"il appelé hors","en":"he called out","tr":"nādā","isWaqf":false},{"position":10,"ar":"وَهُوَ","fr":"tandis qu'il","en":"while he","tr":"wahuwa","isWaqf":false},{"position":11,"ar":"مَكْظُومٌۭ","fr":"(était) affligé","en":"(was) distressed","tr":"makẓūmun","isWaqf":false}]},{"ayah":49,"verseKey":"68:49","juz":29,"arabic":"لَّوْلَآ أَن تَدَٰرَكَهُۥ نِعْمَةٌ مِّن رَّبِّهِۦ لَنُبِذَ بِٱلْعَرَآءِ وَهُوَ مَذْمُومٌ","fr":"N’eût été une grâce qui l’atteignît de la part de son Seigneur, il eût été sans doute jeté, couvert d’ignominie, sur un rivage désert.","en":"If not that a favor [i.e., mercy] from his Lord overtook him, he would have been thrown onto the naked shore while he was censured.","words":[{"position":1,"ar":"لَّوْلَآ","fr":"Si non","en":"If not","tr":"lawlā","isWaqf":false},{"position":2,"ar":"أَن","fr":"que","en":"that","tr":"an","isWaqf":false},{"position":3,"ar":"تَدَٰرَكَهُۥ","fr":"rattrapa lui","en":"overtook him","tr":"tadārakahu","isWaqf":false},{"position":4,"ar":"نِعْمَةٌۭ","fr":"un Faveur","en":"a Favor","tr":"niʿ'matun","isWaqf":false},{"position":5,"ar":"مِّن","fr":"de","en":"from","tr":"min","isWaqf":false},{"position":6,"ar":"رَّبِّهِۦ","fr":"son Seigneur","en":"his Lord","tr":"rabbihi","isWaqf":false},{"position":7,"ar":"لَنُبِذَ","fr":"assurément il irait ont été jeté","en":"surely he would have been thrown","tr":"lanubidha","isWaqf":false},{"position":8,"ar":"بِٱلْعَرَآءِ","fr":"sur (le) naked rivage","en":"onto (the) naked shore","tr":"bil-ʿarāi","isWaqf":false},{"position":9,"ar":"وَهُوَ","fr":"tandis qu'il","en":"while he","tr":"wahuwa","isWaqf":false},{"position":10,"ar":"مَذْمُومٌۭ","fr":"(était) blâma","en":"(was) blamed","tr":"madhmūmun","isWaqf":false}]},{"ayah":50,"verseKey":"68:50","juz":29,"arabic":"فَٱجْتَبَـٰهُ رَبُّهُۥ فَجَعَلَهُۥ مِنَ ٱلصَّـٰلِحِينَ","fr":"Son Seigneur l’élut et le fit du nombre des vertueux.","en":"And his Lord chose him and made him of the righteous.","words":[{"position":1,"ar":"فَٱجْتَبَـٰهُ","fr":"Mais choisit lui","en":"But chose him","tr":"fa-ij'tabāhu","isWaqf":false},{"position":2,"ar":"رَبُّهُۥ","fr":"son Seigneur","en":"his Lord","tr":"rabbuhu","isWaqf":false},{"position":3,"ar":"فَجَعَلَهُۥ","fr":"et fait lui","en":"and made him","tr":"fajaʿalahu","isWaqf":false},{"position":4,"ar":"مِنَ","fr":"de","en":"of","tr":"mina","isWaqf":false},{"position":5,"ar":"ٱلصَّـٰلِحِينَ","fr":"les justes","en":"the righteous","tr":"l-ṣāliḥīna","isWaqf":false}]},{"ayah":51,"verseKey":"68:51","juz":29,"arabic":"وَإِن يَكَادُ ٱلَّذِينَ كَفَرُوا۟ لَيُزْلِقُونَكَ بِأَبْصَـٰرِهِمْ لَمَّا سَمِعُوا۟ ٱلذِّكْرَ وَيَقُولُونَ إِنَّهُۥ لَمَجْنُونٌ","fr":"Il s’en faut de peu que les mécréants ne te vrillent de leurs regards quand ils entendent le (Coran). Ils disent alors : « Ce n’est qu’un dément ! »","en":"And indeed, those who disbelieve would almost make you slip with their eyes [i.e., looks] when they hear the message, and they say, \"Indeed, he is mad.\"","words":[{"position":1,"ar":"وَإِن","fr":"Et certes","en":"And indeed","tr":"wa-in","isWaqf":false},{"position":2,"ar":"يَكَادُ","fr":"irait presque","en":"would almost","tr":"yakādu","isWaqf":false},{"position":3,"ar":"ٱلَّذِينَ","fr":"ceux qui","en":"those who","tr":"alladhīna","isWaqf":false},{"position":4,"ar":"كَفَرُوا۟","fr":"mécroire","en":"disbelieve","tr":"kafarū","isWaqf":false},{"position":5,"ar":"لَيُزْلِقُونَكَ","fr":"assurément faire vous glissez","en":"surely make you slip","tr":"layuz'liqūnaka","isWaqf":false},{"position":6,"ar":"بِأَبْصَـٰرِهِمْ","fr":"avec leur regarder","en":"with their look","tr":"bi-abṣārihim","isWaqf":false},{"position":7,"ar":"لَمَّا","fr":"quand","en":"when","tr":"lammā","isWaqf":false},{"position":8,"ar":"سَمِعُوا۟","fr":"ils entendent","en":"they hear","tr":"samiʿū","isWaqf":false},{"position":9,"ar":"ٱلذِّكْرَ","fr":"le Message","en":"the Message","tr":"l-dhik'ra","isWaqf":false},{"position":10,"ar":"وَيَقُولُونَ","fr":"et ils disent","en":"and they say","tr":"wayaqūlūna","isWaqf":false},{"position":11,"ar":"إِنَّهُۥ","fr":"Certes, il","en":"Indeed, he","tr":"innahu","isWaqf":false},{"position":12,"ar":"لَمَجْنُونٌۭ","fr":"(est) assurément fou","en":"(is) surely mad","tr":"lamajnūnun","isWaqf":false}]},{"ayah":52,"verseKey":"68:52","juz":29,"arabic":"وَمَا هُوَ إِلَّا ذِكْرٌ لِّلْعَـٰلَمِينَ","fr":"Et ce (Coran) n’est rien de moins qu’un Rappel (adressé) à l’Univers !","en":"But it is not except a reminder to the worlds.","words":[{"position":1,"ar":"وَمَا","fr":"Et non","en":"And not","tr":"wamā","isWaqf":false},{"position":2,"ar":"هُوَ","fr":"c'(est)","en":"it (is)","tr":"huwa","isWaqf":false},{"position":3,"ar":"إِلَّا","fr":"mais","en":"but","tr":"illā","isWaqf":false},{"position":4,"ar":"ذِكْرٌۭ","fr":"un Rappel","en":"a Reminder","tr":"dhik'run","isWaqf":false},{"position":5,"ar":"لِّلْعَـٰلَمِينَ","fr":"à les mondes","en":"to the worlds","tr":"lil'ʿālamīna","isWaqf":false}]}]